{"abstract": "Even as Countrywide Financial\u2019s ugly financial results show no signs of abating, Bank of America says it is committed to go through with its takeover plans.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/08/business/08country.html", "snippet": "Even as Countrywide Financial\u2019s ugly financial results show no signs of abating, Bank of America says it is committed to go through with its takeover plans.", "lead_paragraph": "IN the six months since Bank of America announced its plans to take over Countrywide Financial, many investors have doubted that the $4 billion deal for the hobbled mortgage lender would get done. Bank of America has been strangely silent about its plans for merging the two operations, with the exception of a cryptic regulatory filing last month warning that investors should not count on it assuming all of Countrywide\u2019s debt.", "print_section": "BU", "print_page": "1", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2008/06/08/business/08gret.xlarge1.jpg", "height": 350, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2008/06/08/business/08gret.xlarge1.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 350}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2008/06/08/business/08gret.751.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2008/06/08/business/08gret.751.jpg", "thumbnailwidth": 75, "thumbnailheight": 75}}], "headline": {"main": "Bank of America Is Firm on Countrywide Buyout", "kicker": null, "content_kicker": null, "print_headline": "Countrywide\u2019s Buyer Isn\u2019t Blinking", "name": null, "seo": null, "sub": null}, "keywords": [{"name": "subject", "value": "Mergers, Acquisitions and Divestitures", "rank": 1, "major": "N"}, {"name": "organizations", "value":